episode_summary: In this episode, Brittany Ranew shares her journey from a music background to becoming a top-producing REALTOR in St. Petersburg, Florida. She discusses the importance of mindset, personal development, and building a community-focused personal brand through podcasting. Brittany also provides insights on navigating the challenges of the 2023 real estate market by focusing on meaningful conversations and maintaining an abundant mindset.
